    <div class="career-detail">
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Introduction -->
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    </div>
                    Introduction
                </h2>
                <p>Business and entrepreneurship represent the dynamic world of creating, building, and scaling innovative solutions. In today's rapidly evolving economy, entrepreneurs are the driving force behind technological advancement, job creation, and economic growth. This field offers unlimited potential for those with vision, determination, and the willingness to take calculated risks.</p>
                
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">70%</span>
                        <span>Of startups in India are tech-based</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">50K+</span>
                        <span>Startups registered in India</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">₹100K+</span>
                        <span>Average startup funding</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-number">3.5M+</span>
                        <span>Jobs created by startups</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Branches/Specializations -->
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-sitemap"></i>
                    </div>
                    Branches & Specializations
                </h2>
                
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> Tech Startups</h4>
                        <p>SaaS, Mobile Apps, AI/ML, Blockchain, IoT solutions, and software development companies</p>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Software as a Service (SaaS)</li>
                            <li>Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning</li>
                            <li>Mobile Application Development</li>
                            <li>Blockchain Technology</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> E-commerce</h4>
                        <p>Online retail, marketplaces, dropshipping, social commerce platforms</p>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Online Marketplaces</li>
                            <li>D2C Brands</li>
                            <li>Social Commerce</li>
                            <li>B2B E-commerce</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> HealthTech</h4>
                        <p>Telemedicine, health apps, medical devices, wellness platforms</p>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Telemedicine Platforms</li>
                            <li>Health Monitoring Apps</li>
                            <li>Medical Device Innovation</li>
                            <li>Mental Health Solutions</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> EdTech</h4>
                        <p>Online learning, skill development, educational tools and platforms</p>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Online Learning Platforms</li>
                            <li>Skill Development Apps</li>
                            <li>Educational Games</li>
                            <li>Virtual Classrooms</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Green Tech</h4>
                        <p>Clean energy, sustainable solutions, environmental technology</p>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Renewable Energy</li>
                            <li>Waste Management</li>
                            <li>Electric Vehicles</li>
                            <li>Carbon Footprint Solutions</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> FoodTech</h4>
                        <p>Food delivery, agriculture tech, food processing, cloud kitchens</p>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Food Delivery Platforms</li>
                            <li>Cloud Kitchens</li>
                            <li>AgriTech Solutions</li>
                            <li>Food Safety Technology</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="chart-container">
                    <canvas id="sectorsChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Eligibility & Requirements -->
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    Eligibility & Entrance Requirements
                </h2>
                
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i> Educational Background</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Any bachelor's degree (preferred but not mandatory)</li>
                            <li>MBA for advanced business knowledge</li>
                            <li>Technical degree for tech startups</li>
                            <li>Relevant certifications in your domain</li>
                            <li>Online courses in entrepreneurship</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Key Requirements</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Innovative mindset and problem-solving skills</li>
                            <li>Risk-taking ability and resilience</li>
                            <li>Leadership and team management</li>
                            <li>Basic understanding of finance and marketing</li>
                            <li>Strong communication skills</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i> Entrance Exams</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>CAT/MAT for MBA programs</li>
                            <li>GATE for technical entrepreneurship</li>
                            <li>Industry certification exams</li>
                            <li>No formal entrance for direct startup</li>
                            <li>Incubator selection processes</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Technical Skills</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Basic coding knowledge (for tech startups)</li>
                            <li>Digital marketing understanding</li>
                            <li>Data analysis capabilities</li>
                            <li>Project management skills</li>
                            <li>Financial modeling knowledge</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Top Colleges/Incubators -->
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-university"></i>
                    </div>
                    Top Colleges & Incubators
                </h2>
                
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> Tier 1 Incubators</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>SINE (IIT Bombay) - Society for Innovation & Entrepreneurship</li>
                            <li>T-Hub (Hyderabad) - Technology Hub</li>
                            <li>NSRCEL (IIM Bangalore) - NS Raghavan Centre</li>
                            <li>CIIE (IIM Ahmedabad) - Centre for Innovation</li>
                            <li>KTBI (Kochi) - Kerala Technology Business Incubator</li>
                            <li>STEP (IIT Delhi) - Science & Technology Park</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Accelerators</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>Techstars India - Global startup accelerator</li>
                            <li>Axilor Ventures - Early stage venture fund</li>
                            <li>Indian Angel Network - Angel investor network</li>
                            <li>500 Startups India - Venture capital firm</li>
                            <li>Zone Startups India - Corporate accelerator</li>
                            <li>Microsoft Accelerator - Tech startup accelerator</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-school"></i> Top Business Schools</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>IIM Ahmedabad - Entrepreneurship programs</li>
                            <li>IIM Bangalore - Innovation courses</li>
                            <li>ISB Hyderabad - Startup ecosystem</li>
                            <li>XLRI Jamshedpur - Business innovation</li>
