                            <li>MUDRA Loans (up to ₹10L)</li>
                            <li>Stand Up India (₹10L to ₹1Cr)</li>
                            <li>SIDBI Fund of Funds (₹10,000Cr corpus)</li>
                            <li>Tax exemptions for 3 years</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> Competitions & Grants</h4>
                        <ul class="list-styled">
                            <li>National Startup Awards (₹5L prize)</li>
                            <li>Smart India Hackathon (₹1L prize)</li>
                            <li>Nasscom Emerge 50 Program</li>
                            <li>TiE Global Awards</li>
                            <li>University innovation challenges</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Life in Startup Ecosystem -->
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    Life in Startup Ecosystem
                </h2>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> The Startup Lifestyle</h3>
                    <p>Fast-paced, dynamic environment with constant learning, networking opportunities, and the excitement of building something from scratch!</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
